rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0001
rows.name: So, lady knight. What's the plan now?

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Though I do feel like I understand
Adel a bit better now...

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0005
rows.name: Well, Metsu has given us some time.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0006
rows.name:
Our first priority should be to make
sure that the people of Iira are safe.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0007
rows.name:
In the wake of an attack on the capital,
the stability of the country is at its
most precarious.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0008
rows.name:
Alleviating any uneasiness on the part
of the citizens is indeed a most
pressing concern.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0010
rows.name:
And in doing that, perhaps we'll grow
a little stronger, too.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Then let's see what's going on in
the capital and with the resistance.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0012
rows.name:
Thanks for sticking around Minochi.
I'm sure we'll end up getting into a lot
more scrapes before this is all over.

rows.label: campfev11_670_150_msg0013
rows.name: Knowing you, I'm sure we will...
